<L>__{exterior street warburg outside the farmhouse day}
<A>__{he starts back to the regiment, with his comrade, when the man interrupts his reverie by suggesting they divide the five guineas.}
<C>__{private}
<D>__{i should get half.}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{your share is one guinea.}
<A>__{roderick gives him one guinea.}
<C>__{private}
<D>__{he gave you five guineas, and i bloody well expect half.}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{go to the devil.}
<A>__{the private lifting his musket, hits roderick a blow with the butt end of it, which sends him stunned to the ground, allowing his comrade to take the other four guineas from his pocket. recovering his senses, roderick bleeding, with a large wound in the head, has barely time to stagger back to the house where he had just left the lieutenant, when he falls fainting at the door, just as the surgeon exits.}
